description:
When I'm summoned, draw 1.
Then, if you've played at least 10 other cards with different names, grant me +4|+0. <style=Variable></style>
descriptionRaw:
When I'm summoned, draw 1.
Then, if you've played at least 10 other cards with different names, grant me +4|+0.
flavorText: Nothing could stop his escape from those simpering humans. Not even a little water...
name: Subpurrsible

description: When I'm summoned, ALL players draw 1.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, ALL players draw 1.
flavorText: Some officers rely on their instincts to crack a case. Others lean on their contacts. But Officer J.S. Harknor's strength is pure diligence, and paperwork. Lots and lots of paperwork.
name: Veteran Investigator

description:
When drawn, costs 2 less this round.
Deal 3 to a unit.
descriptionRaw:
When drawn, costs 2 less this round.
Deal 3 to a unit.
flavorText:
"Mind trying on these handcuffs, Mr. Berz?"
"What's in it for me?"
"You can keep them."
"...A'right then."
"You're under arrest. Take him away!"
name: Gotcha!

description:
Give an ally +2|+0 this round.
Create a <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link> <link=card.selfRef><style=AssociatedCard>Vault Breaker</style></link> in hand.
descriptionRaw:
Give an ally +2|+0 this round.
Create a Fleeting Vault Breaker in hand.
flavorText: "I let my hands do the talking." - Vi
name: Vault Breaker

description: When you play a 2 cost card, draw 1 and give it <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When you play a 2 cost card, draw 1 and give it Fleeting.
flavorText: "All detectives respond, but a good detective anticipates, and an exemplary detective prevents." - The Warden's Handbook
name: Insightful Investigator

description: When you draw a card, give it <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link> and create an exact copy of it in hand.
descriptionRaw: When you draw a card, give it Fleeting and create an exact copy of it in hand.
flavorText: At age five, she made the world's first multi-frequency sonic knife. While not very practical (she mostly used it to slice sandwiches), it set her on her way to the Wardens' elite Armaments Department.
name: Chief Mechanist Zevi

description: While I'm in play or in hand, grant me +1|+0 when you play another card (max +8|+0). <style=Variable></style>
descriptionRaw: While I'm in play or in hand, grant me +1|+0 when you play another card (max +8|+0).
flavorText: "Enforcer Vi, please! Think of the people! The collateral damage! The PAPERWORK FOR INJURY CLAIMS!" - Insightful Investigator
name: Vi

description: Create in hand a random 2 cost card from your regions. It costs 0 this round.
descriptionRaw: Create in hand a random 2 cost card from your regions. It costs 0 this round.
flavorText: "And thus," Officer Harknor announced, "the trail leads us to..."
name: Trail of Evidence

description:
When drawn, costs 2 less this round.
Grow an ally to 4|4.
descriptionRaw:
When drawn, costs 2 less this round.
Grow an ally to 4|4.
flavorText: "Trouble at the docks! Take these, and give them my regards." - Chief Mechanist Zevi
name: Suit Up!

description: When I <link=vocab.Strike><style=Vocab>strike</style></link> a unit while attacking, deal 5 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: When I strike a unit while attacking, deal 5 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "So! Looks like your buddies are all tuckered out. You wanna tell me where you hid the hextech, or d'ya wanna make friends with the wall, too?"
name: Vi

description:
Give an ally +2|+0 this round.
Create a <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link> <link=card.selfRef><style=AssociatedCard>Vault Breaker</style></link> in hand.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Vi</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Give an ally +2|+0 this round.
Create a Fleeting Vault Breaker in hand.
Create a Vi in your deck.
flavorText: "I let my hands do the talking." - Vi
name: Vi's Vault Breaker

description: When I'm drawn, I cost 1 less this round.
descriptionRaw: When I'm drawn, I cost 1 less this round.
flavorText: Warden Mir's sprinting technique was a running joke among the other enforcers. Warden Kepple didn't get it.
name: Patrol Wardens

flavorText: "MY GRATEST STRENF IS PREBABLE MY COMAND OF DA COMON PEEPUL AN ALSO APPARENLY MY SPELING IS RELLY GUD TO" - Note scribbled in sand
name: Shellshocker

flavorText: "Swear I seen the strangest things over them reefs, Cap'n. Wha's that lunk put in 'em oranges? Tha's what I wanna know..." - Petty Officer
name: Slippery Waverider

description: <style=Variable></style>
flavorText:
"Fear not the blasted beast ye know,
For some survive their thunder,
But what of them that broke the bow,
An' took them poor souls under?" - Found scratched into a Bilgewater tavern beam
name: The Beast Below

flavorText: "...and the idiot said I had hips that 'rolled like the waves'. I told him to cut the flattery, or I'd cut out his tongue."
name: Prowling Cutthroat

description: <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>: Deal 2 to me and summon a <link=card.create><style=AssociatedCard>Powder Monkey</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Round Start: Deal 2 to me and summon a Powder Monkey.
flavorText: "This one's a... souvenir. The crew nabbed it from a crazy old rival of mine. Turns out the fool's ramblings about 'ancient, mysterious powers' weren't too far from the truth..." - Miss Fortune
name: Monkey Idol

description: <link=keyword.Last Breath><sprite name=LastBreath><style=Keyword>Last Breath</style></link>: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Last Breath: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Mischievous little scamps, ain't they? More help than they seem, but word is they've got explosive tempers..." - Syren deckhand
name: Powder Monkey

description:
<link=keyword.PlaySkillMark><sprite name=SkillMark><style=Keyword>Play</style></link>: <link=keyword.Obliterate><style=Keyword>Obliterate</style></link> an enemy with less Health than me.
<style=Variable></style>
descriptionRaw: Play: Obliterate an enemy with less Health than me.
flavorText:
"I was sailing just the other day,
Out beyond Bilgewater Bay,
When, from the depths, she came my way,
the Wing-Eared Sunken Lady..." - "Ballad of the Wing-Eared Sunken Lady"
name: Devourer of the Depths

description: <link=keyword.Obliterate><style=Keyword>Obliterate</style></link> an enemy with less Health than me.
descriptionRaw: Obliterate an enemy with less Health than me.
flavorText:
"She swallowed me whole, me skiff and me soul,
So I'm singin' this song in her belly,
And now I must wait 'til I meet my fate,
In the Wing-Eared Sunken Lady." - "Ballad of the Wing-Eared Sunken Lady"
name: Devour

description: When allies attack, deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: When allies attack, deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Being short gives you a surprising advantage in a fight. Turns out, nobody ever thinks to look down."
name: Crackshot Corsair

description: <link=vocab.Allegiance><style=Vocab>Allegiance</style></link>: <link=keyword.Nab><style=Keyword>Nab</style></link> 1 and create a <link=card.create><style=AssociatedCard>Warning Shot</style></link> in hand.
descriptionRaw: Allegiance: Nab 1 and create a Warning Shot in hand.
flavorText: "Y'know, friends love to help friends out. And you? I like the shine in your eye and the glint on your cutlass! It is a really, really nice cutlass."
name: Yordle Grifter

description:
When I'm summoned, <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 2 and create 2 Treasures in your deck.
<style=Variable></style>
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, Toss 2 and create 2 Treasures in your deck.
flavorText: "These days, there's more treasure 'neath the waves than above 'em, I wager. Would be easy enough pickins, if 'tweren't for her." - Jagged Butcher
name: Shipwreck Hoarder

description:
If I'm <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Tossed</style></link>, draw me instead.
Deal 5 to ALL units.
descriptionRaw:
If I'm Tossed, draw me instead.
Deal 5 to ALL units.
flavorText: The deckhands roared as one and hauled the chains, their treasure now just below the calm waters. Little did they know the Seascraw's legendary cannon had one final act in store.
name: Keelbreaker

description:
Create 5 random cards in hand. They cost 0 and are <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link>.
If I'm <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Tossed</style></link>, draw me instead.
descriptionRaw:
Create 5 random cards in hand. They cost 0 and are Fleeting.
If I'm Tossed, draw me instead.
flavorText: Captain Finn roared out "Ye earned this, boys! Told ye the Tithe was nothin' but coward feed!" Some cheered, but not all. The waters seemed to still, save for the bubbles around the Rancour's hull.
name: Treasure Trove

description: <style=Variable></style>
flavorText: The terrifying beasts burst through the waves and split the hull with vice-like jaws. Though the sailors begged the Bearded Lady for mercy, their captain's greed had already sealed their fate.
name: Vicious Platewyrm

description:
If I'm <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Tossed</style></link>, draw me instead.
Summon 3 <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Vicious Platewyrms</style></link>.
descriptionRaw:
If I'm Tossed, draw me instead.
Summon 3 Vicious Platewyrms.
flavorText: The grizzled captain held his shining quarry aloft and roared out "This'll keep us fer life!" Heady cheers rang out from the crew, while around their brig, the waters began to churn...
name: Platewyrm Egg

flavorText: Lively currents of magic weave through Serpent Isles' reefs, nourishing the sea's extraordinary inhabitants.
name: Bubble Bear

description:
To play me, discard 2.
<link=vocab.Attack><style=Vocab>Attack</style></link>: Draw 2 and give them <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link>.
descriptionRaw:
To play me, discard 2.
Attack: Draw 2 and give them Fleeting.
flavorText: "Ain't nothing to it, most o' the time. Tables are full of fools too busy singing 'emselves hoarse to focus on the game. Not that I mind none. Coin's coin, and it's better in my pocket than theirs."
name: Brash Gambler

description: When I'm summoned, create in hand a random 1 cost spell from your regions.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, create in hand a random 1 cost spell from your regions.
flavorText: Most shallows teem with all kinds of marine life, but none compare to the reefs of the Azure Way. The Way is a magical, otherworldly place, full of wonder.
name: Coral Creatures

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Grant 1 cost allies <link=vocab.Everywhere><style=Vocab>everywhere</style></link> +1|+0.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Grant 1 cost allies everywhere +1|+0.
flavorText: Once she fires, the Hooks have to move fast. Blood in the water brings all manner of company... and none of it is welcome.
name: Jagged Taskmaster

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Heal allies and your Nexus 3, then <link=vocab.Rally><style=Vocab>Rally</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Heal allies and your Nexus 3, then Rally.
flavorText: "All sailors think they so tough! Grr this. Yarr that. Yes yes. Very good. But you still need orange! Make skin pretty, make teeth stay, and make me happy. So you eat, or you swim. Easy."
name: Citrus Courier

description: When I'm summoned, draw a spell that costs 3 or less from your deck.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, draw a spell that costs 3 or less from your deck.
flavorText: Zap once completed the Azure Way circuit in just under three minutes. She even had to dodge the Jilldaw's shattered hull near the end! The currents that day were AWESOME.
name: Zap Sprayfin

description: <link=vocab.Play><style=Vocab>Play</style></link>: Grant an enemy <link=keyword.Vulnerable><sprite name=Vulnerable><style=Keyword>Vulnerable</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Play: Grant an enemy Vulnerable.
flavorText: "I've heard he'll swim miles to find his mark, 'n when he finds 'em, he never misses his shot. Not sure if he's a man or a fish, but it's clear he knows these waters far better'n we do." - Jagged Butcher
name: Razorscale Hunter

description: When I'm summoned, grant all enemies <link=keyword.Vulnerable><sprite name=Vulnerable><style=Keyword>Vulnerable</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, grant all enemies Vulnerable.
flavorText: There may be no law in Bilgewater, yet a handful of brave souls within the city's boisterous walls are unafraid of enforcing their own idea of justice.
name: Sheriff Lariette Rose

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Grant me +1|+1.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Grant me +1|+1.
flavorText: Entry into the Jagged Hooks is a bloody affair. Sailors must prove they know their way around a ship, a fight, and a butcher's block. The most unsavory candidates hit all three marks in a single scrap.
name: Jagged Butcher

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Play <link=card.cast><style=AssociatedCard>Cannon Barrage</style></link> 6 times on randomly targeted enemies.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Play Cannon Barrage 6 times on randomly targeted enemies.
flavorText:
"Sail past the sailors, sail past the wreck,
The battle's already over.
The smoke's cleared the water, their captain's met Rex,
And their ship's ripped an' torn timber." - "Home With You, Sally"
name: Riptide Rex

description:
Deal 2 to a unit.
If it's dead or gone, deal 1 to the enemy Nexus instead.
descriptionRaw:
Deal 2 to a unit.
If it's dead or gone, deal 1 to the enemy Nexus instead.
flavorText: Gangplank's cruelty doesn't end with those who wrong him. To make an enemy of the Saltwater Scourge is to bring death upon everyone you hold dear.
name: Cannon Barrage

description:
<link=vocab.NexusStrike><style=Vocab>Nexus Strike</style></link>: Draw 1.
<style=Variable></style>
descriptionRaw: Nexus Strike: Draw 1.
flavorText:
"Aye aye, they cried, and set off away,
To see to trouble in fair Nashramae,
But nature, she turned, and many did die,
An' the rest are off to see the all-seein' eye!" - "The All-Seeing Eye"
name: Abyssal Eye

description: <link=vocab.Play><style=Vocab>Play</style></link>: Summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Powder Keg</style></link> or a random 1 cost follower.
descriptionRaw: Play: Summon a Powder Keg or a random 1 cost follower.
flavorText: Few things, he learned, could motivate a slacking sailor as promptly as a lit fuse.
name: Petty Officer

description: <link=vocab.Play><style=Vocab>Play</style></link>: Summon a random 1 cost follower.
descriptionRaw: Play: Summon a random 1 cost follower.
flavorText: Few things, he learned, could motivate a slacking sailor as promptly as a lit fuse.
name: Petty Officer

description: <link=vocab.Play><style=Vocab>Play</style></link>: Summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Powder Keg</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Play: Summon a Powder Keg.
flavorText: Few things, he learned, could motivate a slacking sailor as promptly as a lit fuse.
name: Petty Officer

description: When I'm summoned, <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 3.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, Toss 3.
flavorText: It takes a special sort to make complete garbage of perfectly seaworthy gear. But if there's one thing they're good at, it's that. Just that.
name: Dreg Dredgers

description: When I'm summoned, summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Powder Keg</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, summon a Powder Keg.
flavorText: "Aye, we could fight 'em at dawn, when their crew's awake and their cannons are primed. Or we could leave 'em a gift tonight, nice and quiet-like..."
name: Dreadway Deckhand

description: When I'm summoned, draw a <link=card.champ1><style=AssociatedCard>Gangplank</style></link>. Double all damage dealt by your skills, spells and allies.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, draw a Gangplank. Double all damage dealt by your skills, spells and allies.
flavorText:
"Ohhhh, best say yer farewells and draw down the sails,
For the Dreadway's a-comin'.
We're off to the deep, where graves're replete,
'Cuz the Dreadway's a-comin'!" - "The Dreadway's a-Comin'"
name: The Dreadway

description:
When I'm summoned or <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>: Grant me +0|+1 for each card you drew last round, then shuffle my stats.
<style=Variable></style>
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned or Round Start: Grant me +0|+1 for each card you drew last round, then shuffle my stats.
flavorText: One prototype spun three bombs and then exploded. Later models had this early "feature" removed.
name: Slotbot

description: When I'm summoned, summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Golden Narwhal</style></link> for your opponent.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, summon a Golden Narwhal for your opponent.
flavorText: The gold that glitters beneath the waves is neither coin nor ingot, but the lustrous horn of the Slaughter Fleet captain's clever adversary.
name: Hunting Fleet

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Reduce the cost of allies in your hand and deck by 2.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Reduce the cost of allies in your hand and deck by 2.
flavorText: "Come with us on a musical journey! Enjoy tunes from across Runeterra! Just remember--coin's required for entry, and tips are deeply appreciated..." - Show promoter
name: Smooth Soloist

description:
When I'm summoned, draw a <link=card.champ1><style=AssociatedCard>Miss Fortune</style></link>.
While I'm attacking, all your spells and skills deal 1 extra damage.
descriptionRaw:
When I'm summoned, draw a Miss Fortune.
While I'm attacking, all your spells and skills deal 1 extra damage.
flavorText: There's no mistaking the Syren. Her broad pearly sails and polished woodwork leave her as sleek and decorated as the captain at her helm.
name: The Syren

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Grant me 2 random keywords.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Grant me 2 random keywords.
flavorText: "His picture's been on the Bounty Board longer'n most, for he's a greedy, ruthless devil that won't let anyone or anything stand in his way. Worst of all? He's... He's cute, damn it." - Gangplank
name: Plunder Poro

description: When I'm summoned, draw 1 at the next <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link> and give it <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, draw 1 at the next Round Start and give it Fleeting.
flavorText: "It don't make no sense to me. I was knocking 'em in easy, but the last one just... wouldn't go. Not my day, I s'pose..." - Brash Gambler
name: Pool Shark

description: When I'm summoned, grant the <link=vocab.Strongest><style=Vocab>strongest</style></link> enemy <link=keyword.Vulnerable><sprite name=Vulnerable><style=Keyword>Vulnerable</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, grant the strongest enemy Vulnerable.
flavorText: "This your picture? Oof, you're even rougher on the eyes than advertised--let's hope your head's worth my while."
name: Hired Gun

description: When I'm summoned, create a random Sea Monster in hand.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, create a random Sea Monster in hand.
flavorText: The lure of fortune pulls countless crews out beyond the shallows. Those poor souls soon discover how terrifying the waters can be, and why so few return.
name: Jaull Hunters

description: <link=vocab.Play><style=Vocab>Play</style></link>: Transform an ally into a random 5 cost follower.
descriptionRaw: Play: Transform an ally into a random 5 cost follower.
flavorText:
"Marvolio? Where... Where are my hands?"
"I will-a now make-a them appear! Tadaa! Ahem. Ta... daa...!"
"...WHERE ARE MY HANDS?!"
"OKAY, TIME-A TO GO! THANK-A YOU ALL SO VERY MUCH!"
name: Mystifying Magician

flavorText: Legends say a pale, horned whale once stole from the Bearded Lady. As punishment, the Lady covered the greedy creature in glittering gold, so it would forever tempt the avarice of others.
name: Golden Narwhal

description:
When you draw an enemy card, reduce its cost by 1.
<link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: <link=keyword.Nab><style=Keyword>Nab</style></link> 1.
descriptionRaw:
When you draw an enemy card, reduce its cost by 1.
Plunder: Nab 1.
flavorText: "If you want it, I've got it! Even got some 'special stock'.... Just remember, you didn't get it from me!"
name: Black Market Merchant

description: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Captain's orders: bullet to the face!" - Crackshot Corsair
name: Crackshot

description: When I'm summoned, summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Powder Keg</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, summon a Powder Keg.
levelupDescription: You've damaged the enemy Nexus in 5 different rounds<style=Variable></style>.
levelupDescriptionRaw: You've damaged the enemy Nexus in 5 different rounds.
flavorText: "Don't stare too long, lest he catches you lookin'. And don't speak ill of him, for he hears all Bilgewater's whispers. Here he comes. Chin low. Eyes lower." - Dreadway deckhand
name: Gangplank

description:
Deal 1 to anything.
If this kills it, deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Gangplank</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Deal 1 to anything.
If this kills it, deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
Create a Gangplank in your deck.
flavorText: Gangplank's version of mediation is often brief, and always bloody.
name: Gangplank's Parrrley

description:
When I'm summoned or <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>: Summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Powder Keg</style></link>.
<link=keyword.AttackSkillMark><sprite name=SkillMark><style=Keyword>Attack</style></link>: Deal 1 to all enemies and the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw:
When I'm summoned or Round Start: Summon a Powder Keg.
Attack: Deal 1 to all enemies and the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Seen his eyes enough to know. Ain't nothin' but pure anger there. Someday, the boss'll do to Bilgewater what it did to him." - Petty Officer
name: Gangplank

description:
Powder Kegs stack.
All of your spells and skills deal <style=Variable>1</style> extra damage.
Destroy me when your spell or skill damages enemies or the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw:
Powder Kegs stack.
All of your spells and skills deal 1 extra damage.
Destroy me when your spell or skill damages enemies or the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Where there's a keg, there's a way." - Bilgewater saying
name: Powder Keg

description: Deal 1 to all enemies and the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 1 to all enemies and the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Blow 'em to the depths!" - Gangplank
name: Powderful Explosion

description: When allies attack, deal 1 to all battling enemies and the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: When allies attack, deal 1 to all battling enemies and the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "'Miss' Fortune? Out here, you call me 'Captain'."
name: Miss Fortune

description:
Deal 1 to three different randomly targeted enemies or the enemy Nexus.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Miss Fortune</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Deal 1 to three different randomly targeted enemies or the enemy Nexus.
Create a Miss Fortune in your deck.
flavorText: "Guns blazin'!" - Miss Fortune
name: Miss Fortune's Make it Rain

description: When allies attack, deal 1 three times to all battling enemies and the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: When allies attack, deal 1 three times to all battling enemies and the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Most people don't get close enough to see the craftsmanship on these guns. Lucky you."
name: Miss Fortune

description: Deal 1 three times to all battling enemies and the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 1 three times to all battling enemies and the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: Even if you fail to hear the bawdy cries of her crew, there's no way you'll miss her laughter...
name: Bullet Time

description: Deal 1 to all battling enemies and the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 1 to all battling enemies and the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "A little something to remember me by." - Miss Fortune
name: Love Tap

description: When you play a spell, stop all enemy spells and skills targeting me and give me <link=keyword.Elusive><sprite name=Elusive><style=Keyword>Elusive</style></link> this round.
descriptionRaw: When you play a spell, stop all enemy spells and skills targeting me and give me Elusive this round.
flavorText: Of all Bilgewater's legendary figures, Fizz is the most mercurial. Some sailors curse him for the countless brutal wrecks littering the coast...
name: Fizz

description:
When you play a spell, stop all enemy spells and skills targeting me and give me <link=keyword.Elusive><sprite name=Elusive><style=Keyword>Elusive</style></link> this round.
<link=vocab.NexusStrike><style=Vocab>Nexus Strike</style></link>: Create a <link=card.create><style=AssociatedCard>Chum the Waters</style></link> in hand.
descriptionRaw:
When you play a spell, stop all enemy spells and skills targeting me and give me Elusive this round.
Nexus Strike: Create a Chum the Waters in hand.
flavorText: ...while others insist he's just a playful child who safeguards others on their journeys home.
name: Fizz

flavorText: Though there may be ambiguity surrounding Fizz's temperament and intentions, there's absolutely none when it comes to Longtooth.
name: Longtooth

description:
Remove an attacking ally from combat to <link=vocab.Rally><style=Vocab>Rally</style></link>.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Fizz</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Remove an attacking ally from combat to Rally.
Create a Fizz in your deck.
flavorText: "One jump ahead of you!" - Fizz
name: Fizz's Playful Trickster

description: <link=keyword.PlaySkillMark><sprite name=SkillMark><style=Keyword>Play</style></link>: Play a Destiny Card.
descriptionRaw: Play: Play a Destiny Card.
flavorText: "Now, watch the hands, count the cards, and try to keep up. And just remember..."
name: Twisted Fate

description: Deal 2 and <link=keyword.Stun><sprite name=Stunned><style=Keyword>Stun</style></link> the <link=vocab.Strongest><style=Vocab>strongest</style></link> enemy.
descriptionRaw: Deal 2 and Stun the strongest enemy.
flavorText: "All that glitters..." - Twisted Fate
name: Gold Card

description: Each round, the first 3 times you play a card, I play a Destiny Card.
descriptionRaw: Each round, the first 3 times you play a card, I play a Destiny Card.
flavorText: "...it ain't gamblin' if you can't lose."
name: Twisted Fate

description:
Place a card from hand into your deck to draw 2 at the next <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>. Give them <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link>.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Twisted Fate</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Place a card from hand into your deck to draw 2 at the next Round Start. Give them Fleeting.
Create a Twisted Fate in your deck.
flavorText: "I make my own luck." - Twisted Fate
name: Twisted Fate's Pick a Card

description:
Refill 1 spell mana.
Draw 1.
descriptionRaw:
Refill 1 spell mana.
Draw 1.
flavorText: "Blue as the Serpentine." - Twisted Fate
name: Blue Card

description: Deal 1 to all enemies and the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 1 to all enemies and the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Somethin' for everyone." - Twisted Fate
name: Red Card

levelupDescription: When you are <link=keyword.Deep><sprite name=Deep><style=Keyword>Deep</style></link>. <style=Variable></style> When I level up, copy <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Tossed</style></link> allies that cost 4+ into your deck.
levelupDescriptionRaw: When you are Deep.  When I level up, copy Tossed allies that cost 4+ into your deck.
flavorText: "'Twas an anchor what broke the Rancour. Pulled Finn down, an' all. Just a handful of us left now, but night's coming... and the cold. I'm sorry, Ma. You were right. The Titan lives." - Recovered note
name: Nautilus

description:
<link=keyword.Stun><sprite name=Stunned><style=Keyword>Stun</style></link> an enemy.
Place that unit into the enemy deck if you have a <link=card.champCheck><style=AssociatedCard>Nautilus</style></link>.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Nautilus</style></link> into your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Stun an enemy.
Place that unit into the enemy deck if you have a Nautilus.
Create a Nautilus into your deck.
flavorText: "Drag them down..." - Nautilus
name: Nautilus' Riptide

description: Sea Monster allies cost 4 less.
descriptionRaw: Sea Monster allies cost 4 less.
flavorText: All pay the tithe, one way or another.
name: Nautilus

description:
When drawn, costs 1 less this round.
Grant an ally +2|+1.
descriptionRaw:
When drawn, costs 1 less this round.
Grant an ally +2|+1.
flavorText: "Ain't nothin' like a hot streak to keep the chips comin'." - Twisted Fate
name: Pocket Aces

description: Summon 2 random 1 cost followers.
descriptionRaw: Summon 2 random 1 cost followers.
flavorText:
"Oi, Gav--ain't that the fella we're after? Looks like he found a friend."
"Is that... Is that a shark-man, Baz?"
"It's also a bunch more gold, mate. Come on..." - Baz and Gav, aspiring bounty hunters
name: Double Trouble

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: <link=keyword.Recall><style=Keyword>Recall</style></link> ANY follower into your hand.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Recall ANY follower into your hand.
flavorText: "Yer workin' fer us now!" - Petty Officer
name: Strong-arm

description: Grant an enemy <link=keyword.Vulnerable><sprite name=Vulnerable><style=Keyword>Vulnerable</style></link> and summon <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Longtooth</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Grant an enemy Vulnerable and summon Longtooth.
flavorText: "Shark!" - Fizz
name: Chum the Waters

description: Summon 2 <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Powder Kegs</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Summon 2 Powder Kegs.
flavorText: "Barrel!" - Gangplank
name: More Powder!

description:
Deal 1 to anything.
If this kills it, deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw:
Deal 1 to anything.
If this kills it, deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: Gangplank's version of mediation is often brief, and always bloody.
name: Parrrley

description: Summon a random 1 cost follower.
descriptionRaw: Summon a random 1 cost follower.
flavorText:
"Whatcha think, Baz? He don't look so tough."
"Ya sure, Gav? He broke out of prison..."
"Means he's wily, not tough. Come on!" - Baz and Gav, aspiring bounty hunters
name: Jailbreak

description: Place a card from hand into your deck to draw 2 at the next <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>. Give them <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Place a card from hand into your deck to draw 2 at the next Round Start. Give them Fleeting.
flavorText: "I make my own luck." - Twisted Fate
name: Pick a Card

description: Remove an attacking ally from combat to <link=vocab.Rally><style=Vocab>Rally</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Remove an attacking ally from combat to Rally.
flavorText: "One jump ahead of you!" - Fizz
name: Playful Trickster

description:
<link=keyword.Stun><sprite name=Stunned><style=Keyword>Stun</style></link> an enemy.
Place that unit into the enemy deck if you have a <link=card.champCheck><style=AssociatedCard>Nautilus</style></link>.
descriptionRaw:
Stun an enemy.
Place that unit into the enemy deck if you have a Nautilus.
flavorText: "Drag them down..." - Nautilus
name: Riptide

description: This round, grow all allies' Power and Health to the number of other spells you've played this game. <style=Variable></style>
descriptionRaw: This round, grow all allies' Power and Health to the number of other spells you've played this game.
flavorText: The currents and tides around Bilgewater are rightly feared for their strength and sudden turns. But no sailor knows the true power within those waters.
name: Mind Meld

description:
<link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 3.
Deal 7 to a unit.
descriptionRaw:
Toss 3.
Deal 7 to a unit.
flavorText: "If it sinks 'em, it was worth it." - Bilgewater saying
name: Scrapshot

description:
Reduce the cost of Sea Monster allies <link=vocab.Everywhere><style=Vocab>everywhere</style></link> by 1.
Draw a Sea Monster.
descriptionRaw:
Reduce the cost of Sea Monster allies everywhere by 1.
Draw a Sea Monster.
flavorText: Sailors speak in hushed tones of dark days to come; when the seas churn and boil, and unspeakable horrors rise from the waves.
name: Lure of the Depths

description:
Deal 2 to an enemy.
If this kills it, deal 4 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw:
Deal 2 to an enemy.
If this kills it, deal 4 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "I always shoot first." - Miss Fortune
name: Double Up

description:
<link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 2.
Draw 2.
descriptionRaw:
Toss 2.
Draw 2.
flavorText: Flotsam doesn't stay afloat for long. Any seafarer worth their salt has to be able to quickly discern valuable cargo from common junk...
name: Salvage

description:
<link=keyword.Nab><style=Keyword>Nab</style></link> 1.
<link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: <link=keyword.Nab><style=Keyword>Nab</style></link> 1 more.
descriptionRaw:
Nab 1.
Plunder: Nab 1 more.
flavorText: What's mine is mine, and what's yours is... also mine.
name: Pilfered Goods

description: Give an enemy <link=keyword.Vulnerable><sprite name=Vulnerable><style=Keyword>Vulnerable</style></link> this round. If it dies this round, draw 1.
descriptionRaw: Give an enemy Vulnerable this round. If it dies this round, draw 1.
flavorText: "Keep yer chin up and yer spirits high, boy! If the cap'n sees ya saggin', he'll hoist ya up, cut y'open, an' feed ya to the gulls. Now, move yer arse!" - Dreadway deckhand
name: Ye Been Warned

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Draw a random non-champion card from the enemy hand.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Draw a random non-champion card from the enemy hand.
flavorText: "Cards ain't about luck. It's about people. You get the folks across the table to doubt themselves? Might as well take all they've got there and then." - Twisted Fate
name: Sleight of Hand

description: Deal 1 to three different randomly targeted enemies or the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 1 to three different randomly targeted enemies or the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Guns blazin'!" - Miss Fortune
name: Make it Rain

description: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Yer supposed to fire w' the rest of us, lad! That's what a salvo is!" - Petty Officer
name: Warning Shot

description: <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 4.
descriptionRaw: Toss 4.
flavorText: "If it ain't worth its weight, it goes over. Same goes for you lot, 'n all. Now back ta work!" - Petty Officer
name: Jettison

description: When I'm summoned, summon a random 1 cost follower and grant it <link=keyword.Scout><sprite name=Scout><style=Keyword>Scout</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, summon a random 1 cost follower and grant it Scout.
flavorText:
"Lift the light from Mother Serpent
To the clouds, up from the waves.
The sky looks down, with gray eyes earnest,
A calm reflection of her gaze.
She smiles, is at peace..."
- prayer to Nagakaborous
name: Island Navigator

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Get an empty mana gem.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: Get an empty mana gem.
flavorText: The young riders of the Winter's Claw are given a wolf pup the moment they can hold a weapon. Their upbringing is devoted entirely to battle--the wolf trained to savage and maim, and the rider to pillage and steal.
name: Wolfrider

description: Give an enemy <link=keyword.Frostbite><sprite name=Frostbite><style=Keyword>Frostbite</style></link> and <link=keyword.Vulnerable><sprite name=Vulnerable><style=Keyword>Vulnerable</style></link> this round.
descriptionRaw: Give an enemy Frostbite and Vulnerable this round.
flavorText: "These warmbloods wouldn't last a single day in the Freljord!" - Sejuani
name: Caught in the Cold

description: <link=vocab.Play><style=Vocab>Play</style></link>: Give an enemy <link=keyword.Frostbite><sprite name=Frostbite><style=Keyword>Frostbite</style></link> and <link=keyword.Vulnerable><sprite name=Vulnerable><style=Keyword>Vulnerable</style></link> this round.
descriptionRaw: Play: Give an enemy Frostbite and Vulnerable this round.
levelupDescription: You've damaged the enemy Nexus in 5 different rounds<style=Variable></style>.
levelupDescriptionRaw: You've damaged the enemy Nexus in 5 different rounds.
flavorText: While her flail of True Ice is formidable, Sejuani herself is the weapon--forged in the bitter cold of the Freljord and tested against the freezing climes.
name: Sejuani

description: <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>: Deal 1 to EVERYTHING.
descriptionRaw: Round Start: Deal 1 to EVERYTHING.
flavorText:
"They will till their fruitful fields,
They will weakly sow their seeds.
We will set 'most all aflame, 
Winter's Claw takes what it please!" - a Winter's Claw children's rhyme
name: Ember Maiden

description: <link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: I transform into <link=card.transform><style=AssociatedCard>Stormclaw Ursine</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Plunder: I transform into Stormclaw Ursine.
flavorText: The Ursine begin as humans, but give up the familiar trappings of their mortal lives for the feral, savage power granted by the great spirit of the Volibear.
name: Ursine Spiritwalker

description: Other allies with 5+ Power have <link=keyword.Overwhelm><sprite name=Overwhelm><style=Keyword>Overwhelm</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Other allies with 5+ Power have Overwhelm.
flavorText: Fully unleashed, the Ursine shed their humanity and take on the power of the storm. They tear across the frozen steppes, their roars echoing like peals of thunder.
name: Stormclaw Ursine

description:
Grant the top 3 units in your deck +1|+1.
<link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Draw 1 of them.
descriptionRaw:
Grant the top 3 units in your deck +1|+1.
Plunder: Draw 1 of them.
flavorText: "Share and share alike." - Ruthless Raider
name: Shared Spoils

description:
When I'm summoned, Draw a <link=card.champ1><style=AssociatedCard>Sejuani</style></link>.
<link=vocab.Plunder><style=Vocab>Plunder</style></link>: Double the Power and Health of allies in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
When I'm summoned, Draw a Sejuani.
Plunder: Double the Power and Health of allies in your deck.
flavorText: "When Spring brings weather just warm enough for us to plant, it also brings longboats... and the grain that started plentiful grows sparse." - Avarosan Hearthguard
name: The Tuskraider

description:
Give an ally +3|+4 this round.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Sejuani</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Give an ally +3|+4 this round.
Create a Sejuani in your deck.
flavorText: "Embrace the beast within!" - Sejuani
name: Sejuani's Fury of the North

description:
<link=vocab.Play><style=Vocab>Play</style></link>: Give an enemy <link=keyword.Frostbite><sprite name=Frostbite><style=Keyword>Frostbite</style></link> and <link=keyword.Vulnerable><sprite name=Vulnerable><style=Keyword>Vulnerable</style></link> this round.
Each round, the first time you damage the enemy Nexus, <link=keyword.Frostbite><sprite name=Frostbite><style=Keyword>Frostbite</style></link> all enemies.
descriptionRaw:
Play: Give an enemy Frostbite and Vulnerable this round.
Each round, the first time you damage the enemy Nexus, Frostbite all enemies.
flavorText: "Lay them low! Show them the Freljord belongs to the Winter's Claw!"
name: Sejuani

description: Give an ally +3|+4 this round.
descriptionRaw: Give an ally +3|+4 this round.
flavorText: "Embrace the beast within!" - Sejuani
name: Fury of the North

flavorText: The Winter's Claw has no equal in the Freljord, and all know the ferocity of these merciless raiders. Once their bloodlust takes over, one can only pray for a quick death.
name: Ruthless Raider

description: Create 2 random Poros and 2 <link=card.snaxRef><style=AssociatedCard>Poro Snax</style></link> in hand.
descriptionRaw: Create 2 random Poros and 2 Poro Snax in hand.
flavorText:
"When you wish upon a poro,
An' look at da night sky,
You'll see da snax among da stars,
All sparkly in our eyes" - Ingvar the Younger
name: Aurora Porealis

description:
When I'm summoned, draw a <link=card.champ1><style=AssociatedCard>Swain</style></link>.
<link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus 3 times.
descriptionRaw:
When I'm summoned, draw a Swain.
Round Start: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus 3 times.
flavorText: When the Ionian locals saw it looming on the horizon, they thought it a monster. They were not far from the truth--the steel warship is terrifying, the greatest feat of Noxian naval engineering yet.
name: The Leviathan

description: <link=vocab.NexusStrike><style=Vocab>Nexus Strike</style></link>: Deal 3 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Nexus Strike: Deal 3 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "A power beyond mortal understanding gave me the vision to see what most cannot. I peer through the darkness others fear."
name: Swain

description:
When you deal non-combat damage to the enemy Nexus, <link=keyword.Stun><sprite name=Stunned><style=Keyword>Stun</style></link> the <link=vocab.Strongest><style=Vocab>strongest</style></link> backrow enemy.
<link=vocab.NexusStrike><style=Vocab>Nexus Strike</style></link>: Deal 3 to all enemies and the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw:
When you deal non-combat damage to the enemy Nexus, Stun the strongest backrow enemy.
Nexus Strike: Deal 3 to all enemies and the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "No sacrifice is too great to see my vision for Noxus fulfilled."
name: Swain

description:
Deal 4 to a unit if it's damaged or <link=keyword.Stun><sprite name=Stunned><style=Keyword>Stunned</style></link>.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Swain</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Deal 4 to a unit if it's damaged or Stunned.
Create a Swain in your deck.
flavorText: Listen. Can you hear them? The thunder of a thousand beating wings.
name: Swain's Ravenous Flock

description: <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Round Start: Deal 1 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: The elders voice was surprisingly calm. What, pray tell, he inquired, is the point of gathering stones to build higher walls, when the Noxians always manage to toss them back over?
name: Citybreaker

description: <link=vocab.Attack><style=Vocab>Attack</style></link>: <link=keyword.Stun><sprite name=Stunned><style=Keyword>Stun</style></link> all damaged enemies.
descriptionRaw: Attack: Stun all damaged enemies.
flavorText: For generations, we have been subjugated. It was not until Noxus took our lands that we finally understood true freedom. That is why I fight for the empire.
name: Aurok Glinthorn

description: Deal 4 to a unit if it's damaged or <link=keyword.Stun><sprite name=Stunned><style=Keyword>Stunned</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Deal 4 to a unit if it's damaged or Stunned.
flavorText: Listen. Can you hear them? The thunder of a thousand beating wings.
name: Ravenous Flock

description: <link=keyword.PlaySkillMark><sprite name=SkillMark><style=Keyword>Play</style></link>: Deal 1 to an ally to deal 2 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Play: Deal 1 to an ally to deal 2 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Quick and quiet, 'til the boom."
name: Imperial Demolitionist

description: Deal 3 to an ally to deal 3 to anything.
descriptionRaw: Deal 3 to an ally to deal 3 to anything.
flavorText: "Sacrifices must be made." - Jericho Swain
name: Noxian Fervor

description: Enemies with 4 or less Power cannot damage me.
descriptionRaw: Enemies with 4 or less Power cannot damage me.
flavorText: "There's no stopping a warbeast once it's in motion--best just to get out of the way." - Basilisk Rider
name: Armored Tuskrider

description: Deal 1 to an ally to deal 2 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 1 to an ally to deal 2 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: The hazards of using black powder are a small price to pay for tactical victory.
name: Black Powder Grenade

description: Deal 2 to an enemy and 1 to the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: Deal 2 to an enemy and 1 to the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Try to die with dignity." - Swain
name: Death's Hand

flavorText: "A siege is easy, if you've the tools. The 'breakers bring 'em out, and the ballistae bring 'em down." - Siege Engineer
name: Iron Ballista

flavorText: It's true what they say--pets look like their owners.
name: Loyal Badgerbear

flavorText: A ranger recruit spends months in the forest with their companions, learning to predict their stag's every move. They must be patient, but once the two have bonded, nothing can come between them.
name: Greathorn Companion

flavorText: "I swore an oath to protect this forest, and all who seek shelter within it."
name: Greenfang Warden

description: When I'm summoned, summon <link=card.create><style=AssociatedCard>Valor</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, summon Valor.
flavorText: "She's always been a fearless ranger-knight, our Quinn--and with Valor by her side and in the skies, the two are unstoppable." - Genevieve Elmheart, ranger-knight
name: Quinn

description:
Summon <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Valor</style></link>.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Quinn</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Summon Valor.
Create a Quinn in your deck.
flavorText: "He's in my hair! HE'S IN MY HAIR!" - Legion Marauder
name: Quinn's Blinding Assault

flavorText: Those who meet him swear they see a glimmer of something more in those sharp eyes, a shrewd intelligence that far surpasses any ordinary bird of prey.
name: Valor

description: <link=vocab.Attack><style=Vocab>Attack</style></link>: Summon <link=card.create><style=AssociatedCard>Valor</style></link> <link=keyword.Challenger><sprite name=Challenger><style=Keyword>Challenging</style></link> the <link=vocab.Strongest><style=Vocab>strongest</style></link> enemy.
descriptionRaw: Attack: Summon Valor Challenging the strongest enemy.
flavorText: "I'll follow your lead, Valor!"
name: Quinn

description: <link=keyword.Last Breath><sprite name=LastBreath><style=Keyword>Last Breath</style></link>: Summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Loyal Badgerbear</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Last Breath: Summon a Loyal Badgerbear.
flavorText: Betrand got his start in the Bandle Scouts. He got all the badges except for 'Cheerful Demeanor'."
name: Grizzled Ranger

description: Grant an ally "I can't take damage or die".
descriptionRaw: Grant an ally "I can't take damage or die".
flavorText: Ignoring the pain of her wounded leg, the ranger stood once more, sword aloft. It was not just her own resolve that kept her standing, but the resolve of Demacia itself.
name: Unyielding Spirit

description: Summon <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Valor</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Summon Valor.
flavorText: "He's in my hair! HE'S IN MY HAIR!" - Legion Marauder
name: Blinding Assault

description: When I'm summoned, give other allies +1|+1 this round.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, give other allies +1|+1 this round.
flavorText: To see the rangers of Demacia in battle is inspiring. They fight as one--human and animal, side by side, fiercely determined and utterly inseparable.
name: Genevieve Elmheart

description: Give all allies <link=keyword.Tough><sprite name=Tough><style=Keyword>Tough</style></link> this round.
descriptionRaw: Give all allies Tough this round.
flavorText: "When the enemy draws near, do not let fear into your hearts, for the trees themselves protect us." - Greenfang Warden
name: Ranger's Resolve

description: Pick an enemy. 2 allies <link=vocab.Strike><style=Vocab>strike</style></link> it one after another.
descriptionRaw: Pick an enemy. 2 allies strike it one after another.
flavorText: "With me, as one!" - Greenfang Warden
name: Concerted Strike

description:
<link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 3.
Heal all allies 3.
descriptionRaw:
Toss 3.
Heal all allies 3.
flavorText: "These Isles will be cleansed." - Maokai
name: Sap Magic

description: When I'm summoned, <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 3.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, Toss 3.
flavorText: "The great treant has continued showing... creatures. This one... to spread life as she wanders... remarkable such... here. These are Blessed Isles indeed!" - Recovered journal
name: Deadbloom Wanderer

description: Each round, the first time you summon another ally, <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 2 and summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Sapling</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Each round, the first time you summon another ally, Toss 2 and summon a Sapling.
levelupDescription: Your units have died or your cards have been <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Tossed</style></link> 25 times.<style=Variable></style>
levelupDescriptionRaw: Your units have died or your cards have been Tossed 25 times.
flavorText: These cursed lands would not break Maokai. The treant's commitment ran too deep, and his fury burned too bright, for anything to stand in his way.
name: Maokai

flavorText: "Life here so effortless. Verdant forests... to sprout overnight quite exquisite. What a treasure this land is. Must preserve generations." - Recovered journal
name: Sapling

description:
<link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 3.
Heal all allies 3.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Maokai</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Toss 3.
Heal all allies 3.
Create a Maokai in your deck.
flavorText: "These Isles will be cleansed." - Maokai
name: Maokai's Sap Magic

description:
When I Level Up, <link=keyword.Obliterate><style=Keyword>Obliterate</style></link> the enemy deck, leaving 4 non-champions.
<link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>: Summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Sapling</style></link>.
descriptionRaw:
When I Level Up, Obliterate the enemy deck, leaving 4 non-champions.
Round Start: Summon a Sapling.
flavorText: He would destroy the blight within these isles, and restore its long-lost life.
name: Maokai

description: <link=keyword.Last Breath><sprite name=LastBreath><style=Keyword>Last Breath</style></link>: <link=vocab.Toss><style=Vocab>Toss</style></link> 2 and heal your Nexus 2.
descriptionRaw: Last Breath: Toss 2 and heal your Nexus 2.
flavorText: "...remarkable species same creature I found as a child... not a day older! I wonder next town. Perhaps these wonderful fellows will live forever!" - Recovered journal
name: Thorny Toad

description:
Sea Monster allies have <link=keyword.Fearsome><sprite name=Fearsome><style=Keyword>Fearsome</style></link>. 
<link=vocab.Attack><style=Vocab>Attack</style></link>: Give enemies -2|-0 this round.
<style=Variable></style>
descriptionRaw:
Sea Monster allies have Fearsome. 
Attack: Give enemies -2|-0 this round.
flavorText: They realized the danger too late. The titanic beast opened its gaping maw and surged toward them. The hunters could only wait for death as the endless teeth slowly crunched through their ship.
name: Terror of the Tides

description: When another ally dies, <link=keyword.Drain><style=Keyword>drain</style></link> 1 from the enemy Nexus.
descriptionRaw: When another ally dies, drain 1 from the enemy Nexus.
flavorText: "Bumped into Niven this... the new ferryman! He rowed us... to... He can certainly hold a tune! Before... must invite him to supper soon." - Recovered journal
name: Neverglade Collector

description: When you summon a follower, kill it to summon an <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Overgrown Snapvine</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When you summon a follower, kill it to summon an Overgrown Snapvine.
flavorText:
"Today... another remarkable... surfaced around... children quite scared. But... posed no threat. Nuzzled... quite a trusting creature. Must forage them more berries!"
- Recovered journal
name: Overgrown Snapvine

description: <link=vocab.Play><style=Vocab>Play</style></link>: Kill an ally to summon 2 <link=card.create><style=AssociatedCard>Saplings</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Play: Kill an ally to summon 2 Saplings.
flavorText: "Every heart is a garden where roots may take hold!"
name: Blighted Caretaker

description: The first time an ally dies, grant me +2|+2.
descriptionRaw: The first time an ally dies, grant me +2|+2.
flavorText: The creatures of the Shadow Isles shed sentimentality long ago. They all must eat.
name: Barkbeast

description: Summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Sapling</style></link> at the next <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Summon a Sapling at the next Round Start.
flavorText: "Wheeeeeeee!" - Sapling
name: Sapling Toss

description:
Give an ally <link=keyword.Challenger><sprite name=Challenger><style=Keyword>Challenger</style></link> this round.
Create a <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link> <link=card.secondSpell><style=AssociatedCard>Resonating Strike</style></link> in hand.
descriptionRaw:
Give an ally Challenger this round.
Create a Fleeting Resonating Strike in hand.
flavorText: "Master yourself..." - Lee Sin
name: Sonic Wave

description: Give an ally +2|+0 this round.
descriptionRaw: Give an ally +2|+0 this round.
flavorText: "...master the enemy." - Lee Sin
name: Resonating Strike

description: When I'm <link=keyword.Recall><style=Keyword>Recalled</style></link>, transform me into <link=card.cardRef><style=AssociatedCard>Concussive Palm</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: When I'm Recalled, transform me into Concussive Palm.
flavorText: "A student must move with grace, for the Dragon's breath created the wind and waves which brought motion to our world." - Teachings of the Dragon
name: Tail of the Dragon

description: When I'm summoned, create a <link=card.create><style=AssociatedCard>Dragon's Protection</style></link> in hand.
descriptionRaw: When I'm summoned, create a Dragon's Protection in hand.
flavorText: "A student must act with compassion, for the Dragon nurtured the First Lands, and graced them with warmth and life." - Teachings of the Dragon
name: Scales of the Dragon

description: Grant an ally +0|+3.
descriptionRaw: Grant an ally +0|+3.
flavorText: "The Dragon will keep you safe." - Scales of the Dragon
name: Dragon's Protection

description:
When you play a spell, give me <link=keyword.Challenger><sprite name=Challenger><style=Keyword>Challenger</style></link> this round.
If you play another, give me <link=keyword.Barrier><sprite name=Barrier><style=Keyword>Barrier</style></link> this round.
descriptionRaw:
When you play a spell, give me Challenger this round.
If you play another, give me Barrier this round.
flavorText: "The Dragon aids the worthy. To the weary, it gives vigor. To the sick, comfort. To the lost, light. To the shaken, balance..."
name: Lee Sin

description:
Give an ally <link=keyword.Challenger><sprite name=Challenger><style=Keyword>Challenger</style></link> this round.
Create a <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link> <link=card.secondSpell><style=AssociatedCard>Resonating Strike</style></link> in hand.
Create a <link=card.level1><style=AssociatedCard>Lee Sin</style></link> in your deck.
descriptionRaw:
Give an ally Challenger this round.
Create a Fleeting Resonating Strike in hand.
Create a Lee Sin in your deck.
flavorText: "Master yourself..." - Lee Sin
name: Lee Sin's Sonic Wave

description:
When you play a spell, give me <link=keyword.Challenger><sprite name=Challenger><style=Keyword>Challenger</style></link> this round.
If you play another, give me <link=keyword.Barrier><sprite name=Barrier><style=Keyword>Barrier</style></link> this round.
I <link=card.attackSpell><style=AssociatedCard>Dragon's Rage</style></link> enemies that I <link=keyword.Challenger><sprite name=Challenger><style=Keyword>Challenge</style></link>.
descriptionRaw:
When you play a spell, give me Challenger this round.
If you play another, give me Barrier this round.
I Dragon's Rage enemies that I Challenge.
flavorText: "...But for the tyrant, the Dragon breathes fire."
name: Lee Sin

description:
An ally kicks an enemy into the enemy Nexus, <link=vocab.Strike><style=Vocab>striking</style></link> both.
If the enemy survives, <link=keyword.Recall><style=Keyword>Recall</style></link> it.
descriptionRaw:
An ally kicks an enemy into the enemy Nexus, striking both.
If the enemy survives, Recall it.
flavorText: "The Dragon must be unleashed, or it will consume me from within." - Lee Sin
name: Dragon's Rage

flavorText: "A student must strive with all their might, for the Dragon pulled the earth from beneath the waves, and gave us a land to call home." - Teachings of the Dragon
name: Horns of the Dragon

description: <link=vocab.RoundStart><style=Vocab>Round Start</style></link>: Summon a <link=card.summon><style=AssociatedCard>Dragonling</style></link> if you played 2+ spells last round<style=Variable></style>.
descriptionRaw: Round Start: Summon a Dragonling if you played 2+ spells last round.
flavorText:
"A student must think with clarity, for the Dragon draws the sun across our skies, and reveals the world around us."
- Teachings of the Dragon
name: Eye of the Dragon

description: Summon me from hand the first time you've played 2 spells each round.
descriptionRaw: Summon me from hand the first time you've played 2 spells each round.
flavorText: "A student must listen with focus, for the Dragon roared the first sounds, and blessed our young spirits with the gift of magic." - Teachings of the Dragon
name: Claws of the Dragon

flavorText: "The spirit gives to those who listen." - Eye of the Dragon
name: Dragonling

description: <link=keyword.Stun><sprite name=Stunned><style=Keyword>Stun</style></link> an enemy to summon a <link=card.cardRef><style=AssociatedCard>Tail of the Dragon</style></link>.
descriptionRaw: Stun an enemy to summon a Tail of the Dragon.
flavorText: "You did not see me leave, nor will you see me return." - Tail of the Dragon
name: Concussive Palm

description: <link=keyword.Recall><style=Keyword>Recall</style></link> an ally to create a <link=keyword.Fleeting><sprite name=Fleeting><style=Keyword>Fleeting</style></link> <link=card.secondSpell><style=AssociatedCard>Return</style></link> in hand.
descriptionRaw: Recall an ally to create a Fleeting Return in hand.
flavorText: The first Noxians to set foot on the Ionian beaches found a weak and unprepared enemy. Countless were slaughtered, but a handful managed to make their way to safety...
name: Retreat

description:
An ally kicks an enemy into the enemy Nexus, <link=vocab.Strike><style=Vocab>striking</style></link> the enemy then the enemy Nexus.
If the enemy survives, <link=keyword.Recall><style=Keyword>Recall</style></link> it.
descriptionRaw:
An ally kicks an enemy into the enemy Nexus, striking the enemy then the enemy Nexus.
If the enemy survives, Recall it.
flavorText: "The Dragon must be unleashed, or it will consume me from within." - Lee Sin
name: Dragon's Rage

description: Summon an ally that costs 3 or less from hand.
descriptionRaw: Summon an ally that costs 3 or less from hand.
flavorText: ...and how they rallied. The survivors soon gathered their forces, found their center, and showed the invaders the resilient spirit of the First Lands.
name: Return

description:
Costs 2 less if you played 2+ spells last round.
Draw 2 other spells.
descriptionRaw:
Costs 2 less if you played 2+ spells last round.
Draw 2 other spells.
flavorText: Meditation is a journey with no destination--a path that can only be followed by getting lost along the way.
name: Deep Meditation
